@startuml statemac
title State Machine for API Interactions

[*] --> Start

Start --> PhoneNumberSubmitted : User submits phone number
PhoneNumberSubmitted --> RateLimitExceeded : Rate limit breached
PhoneNumberSubmitted --> VerificationCodeSent : Phone number validated

RateLimitExceeded --> Start : Wait until rate limit resets

VerificationCodeSent --> VerificationPending : SMS sent successfully
VerificationCodeSent --> RetryMechanism : SMS failure

RetryMechanism --> VerificationCodeSent : Retry SMS
RetryMechanism --> Start : Max retries reached

VerificationPending --> CodeExpired : Code expires
VerificationPending --> CodeVerified : User enters valid code
VerificationPending --> RetryMechanism : Invalid code

CodeExpired --> VerificationCodeSent : User requests a new code
CodeExpired --> Start : User abandons the process

CodeVerified --> [*] : Verification successful

@enduml
